JUST PULLED IN TO SPENCEVILLE.

15
00:01:09,802 --> 00:01:11,202
COME ON, YOU GOT
TO CHOOSE.

16
00:01:11,270 --> 00:01:12,637
ALL RIGHT, FINE.

17
00:01:12,705 --> 00:01:14,238
UM, I GUESS I'D
RATHER HAVE

18
00:01:14,306 --> 00:01:16,007
