GOT ME THINKING.

46
00:02:20,506 --> 00:02:23,441
I MEAN, WHY AREN'T THERE PEOPLE
LIVING ON MERCURY RIGHT NOW?

47
00:02:23,509 --> 00:02:25,076
WELL, FOR ONE THING,
IT'S 800 DEGREES.

48
00:02:25,143 --> 00:02:27,078
