LIKE, TWO SECONDS.

49
00:02:27,145 --> 00:02:28,646
NO. IF WE'RE WEARING,
LIKE, SPECIAL SUITS,

50
00:02:28,681 --> 00:02:30,081
LIKE NICK NOLTE
AND MARTIN LAWRENCE.

51
00:02:30,148 --> 00:02:33,884
P.S., THEY'D BE GREAT IN
"THE DOUG AND DEACON STORY."

52
00:02:33,952 --> 00:02:36,170
