ABOUT WHAT WE DID ON THE BEACH.

67
00:03:10,071 --> 00:03:12,273
ANYWAY, YOU GOT MY
NUMBER. GIVE ME A CALL.

68
00:03:17,046 --> 00:03:18,663
TALK TO ME, PLAYER.

69
00:03:20,633 --> 00:03:24,753
